      <title>智利总统博里克努力打击犯罪，谋杀案减少</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-22/chile-murders-decline-as-boric-works-to-get-upper-hand-on-crime</link>
      <description><![CDATA[智利凶杀案继前一年激增后，2023 年下降了 6%，为总统加布里埃尔·博里奇 (Gabriel Boric) 政府打击犯罪的斗争提供了急需的喘息机会。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-22/chile-murders-decline-as-boric-works-to-get-upper-hand-on-crime</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 20:02:46 GMT</pubDate>
